Launch a VM and install docker,K3S,prometheus,grafana,node exporter and k6 load testing tool.
Create a Dockerfile and kubernetes-deploy.yaml file in the github repository.
Create a .github/workflow directory and create a ci-cd.yaml file in the directory and write the script for autobuild and deployment.
Access prometheus and grafana through internet.
Using promQL create dashboards in grafana for monitoring CPU,memory usage, and downtime and create alerts for each.
Create a load_test.js file in the VM and run it using 'k6 run load_test.js' command.
